<DocsPageTitle Path="Extensions/SVG Chart Trendlines">
    Blazorise SVG Chart Trendlines
</DocsPageTitle>

<DocsPageLead>
    Calculate and render trendlines directly in SVG charts.
</DocsPageLead>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    SVG chart trendlines can be declared as child components with <Code>SvgChartTrendline</Code> or supplied through <Code>SvgChartOptions.Trendlines</Code>. Each trendline targets a source series by name.
</DocsPageParagraph>

<DocsPageSubtitle>
    Examples
</DocsPageSubtitle>

<DocsPageSection>
    <DocsPageSectionHeader Title="Declarative trendline">
        Add a trendline to a chart by declaring <Code>SvgChartTrendline</Code> inside the chart.
    </DocsPageSectionHeader>
